Subject: Re: [T2] bus towing capacity

Yes, when equipped with a proper hitch receiver, your truck has a towing
capacity of 1200 lbs. Just go slow and use your gears to slow down. Your
brakes are designed to slow down a payload of 2000 lbs (1 ton) if they are
in good condition, so towing a Beetle is within their parameters.

Jon Stiles

